{"data":[{"id":564086821,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"da50d210a4715bc730bb16f981619d48","url_token":"li-ji-chang-77","name":"一只汪仔","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79166778cd05df4d8209f8cd5af7ade5_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-79166778cd05df4d8209f8cd5af7ade5_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/da50d210a4715bc730bb16f981619d48","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":1,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/564086821","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546328768,"updated_time":1546328768,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e首先一个高中生能主动踏入数学领域表达自己的想法这是好的，但是这位同学很明显目的就不是能够为当今数学研究做些什么，而是一种投机行为。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e做了这件事我能得到什么，我能被清华北大的数学系保送么。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e个人觉得这才是这位同学心里的想法，之前都没人做到，如果我能够做到，我是不是能被保送，我是不是能在数学史上留下自己的名字，然后被世人称赞，一个高中生居然能够解决这么难的数学难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可能这是一些青少年的中二病，不甘于自己的现状，希望从废柴变为写进历史的人物。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他只想象了完成这件事之后自己能够得到什么，但是没有想到过完成这件事情的难度。“初生牛犊不怕虎”挺贴切的，高中水平的数学知识深度没有让他知道数学领域的浩瀚，没有让他知道完成这件事情的难度和为什么至今为止这么多学识渊博的数学家都没能够解决这个数学难题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e参考\u003cb\u003e陈景润\u003c/b\u003e先生的意见，哥德巴赫、费尔马大定理等著名的数学难题是不适宜甚至不可能用初等数论证明出来的，并希望年轻人不要浪费时间在用初等数论证明这种数学难题上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cb\u003e量变引起质变，\u003c/b\u003e在实现某个目标或者梦想的时候，需要的不是什么投机行为，而是自身不断的积累，最终一个蜕变的过程。\u003cb\u003e量变是质变的必要准备，质变是量变的必然结果。\u003c/b\u003e如果真的想要去清华北大的话，努力学习提升自我才是捷径，而不是所谓的「证明」了某个定理，解决了别人倾尽一生都难以解决的问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然还是鼓励所有对数学科研感兴趣的人保持自己的热情，数学领域的大厦仍然需要很多年轻的有才华的人才来建设。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"首先一个高中生能主动踏入数学领域表达自己的想法这是好的，但是这位同学很明显目的就不是能够为当今数学研究做些什么，而是一种投机行为。做了这件事我能得到什么，我能被清华北大的数学系保送么。个人觉得这才是这位同学心里的想法，之前都没人做到，如果…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=1124\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission